{
    "title": "Apaga o fogo Mané",
    "artist": "Adoniran Barbosa",
    "composer": "Adoniran Barbosa",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Inês saiu dizendo que ia comprar um pavio pro lampião</span>\n                                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pode me esperar Mané que eu já volto já</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Acendi o fogão, botei a água pra esquentar</span>\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>                                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E fui pro portão só pra ver Inês chegar</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Anoiteceu e ela não voltou</span>\n                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7/5-\">Em7/5-</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fui pra rua feito louco pra saber o que aconteceu</span>\n                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Procurei na Central, procurei no Hospital e no xadrez</span>\n                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Andei a cidade inteira e não encontrei Inês</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Voltei pra casa triste demais o que Inês me fez não se faz</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E no chão bem perto do fogão</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7/5-\">Em7/5-</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Encontrei um papel escrito assim</span>\n                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pode apagar o fogo mané que eu não volto mais</span>\n                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pode apagar o fogo mané que eu não volto mais</span>\n",
